  "prompt": "What is one decision you never regretted?",
  "response": "One decision I\u2019ve never regretted (and one that many people often reflect on positively) is investing in meaningful relationships\u2014whether it\u2019s with family, friends, or loved ones. Prioritizing time, effort, and care to nurture these connections often leads to a sense of fulfillment, support, and joy that\u2019s irreplaceable. Whether it\u2019s choosing to spend quality time with someone, forgiving a misunderstanding, or simply being present, these choices often yield long-term happiness and personal growth. What about you? Is there a decision in your life that stands out as something you\u2019ve never regretted?",
